description:
The Detective was drinking this
before he was killed. Could it\nhave been drugged?
name: Overturned Wine \nBottle

description:
Whoever killed the Detective 
also took his eye. They must \nknow what his powers are.
name: Missing Eye

description:
The Detective was stabbed in the
back. The killer knew to attack \nfrom where they couldn't be seen.
name: Murder Wound

description:
There are strange patterns in
the bloodstains around the \nDetective. Was he moved after\nhe was killed?
name: Drag Marks

description:
The Detective's satchel has been
searched! It's not completely\nempty but some documents are\nmissing.
name: Looted Satchel

description:
Our original tickets don't match
the room we ended up in. Were we\nmoved on purpose?
name: Old Tickets

description:
This leads into the next
passenger car. That must be \nwhere I'll find the cat.
name: Trail of \nFish Crumbs
